{"tid":2139439,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有分析指疫苗面世前經濟復蘇道路不平坦","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T09:28:22.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d50fe81d1f7c0c1dc38b957a8561033f1c45d5f7","tid":2139439,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"有分析指疫苗面世前經濟復蘇道路不平坦<br />\n2020-08-04 HKT 17:19<br />\n<br />\n&quot;華僑永亨經濟師李若凡相信，上半年經濟已渡過最壞時期。但近日部分地區再爆發疫情，相信疫苗面世前疫情都會反覆，令下半年經濟復蘇道路不平坦，增長較緩慢。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;李若凡指，部分國家因為公共財政惡化相繼被下調評級或展望，外界開始憂慮部分經濟體是否仍有空間推出新的刺激措施。其中，美國的額外失業補貼月底到期，如果在休會前仍未推出新方案，將令刺激措施出現斷崖，引致更多企業面臨倒閉。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541776-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541776-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4YdxOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=9edb3e94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541776-20200804.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d6dc9946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541776-20200804.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}